{"tid":2478130,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–頭髮幹細胞的三個階段","createTime":"2021-04-06T21:47:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T18:55:44.000Z","uid":38861,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"24c9fd7c8e7519b554a35e0ccb89644877f08b33","tid":2478130,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T21:47:48.000Z","msg":"頭髮一直也是不少人所關注的議題，而頭髮的生長，實情跟幹細胞(Stem cell)息息相關。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZQkqBaD9SfRPEVcwnuPmQjDR5t37ioDBrLjsH48sTQNW?filename=odQoAix.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FodQoAix.jpg&h=db429a16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）頭髮的生長，是由位於髮囊底部名為hair-follicle stem cells (HFSCs)的幹細胞產生出來。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRVSuTBAye5FUsxaadh3aZ2tnxZeuM5kVqqFKH5TXjDep?filename=XzNN1YA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXzNN1YA.jpg&h=20dcf18e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這些幹細胞會不斷地進行三個階段的循環，分別為anagen、catagen以及telogen。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）當anagen發生的時候，HFSCs幹細胞就會開始進行自我複製，經一系列的程序後便會導致毛髮生長;這階段可持續進行數年。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcW7Q5dw7eoekkfiG78NdQLxHCvi7tULZLvmZAUbmu2SS?filename=e6a71YD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe6a71YD.jpg&h=bcedcbaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而當到達catagen的時候，毛髮便會停止生長，但依舊維持原位。<br />\n<br />\n之後便會進入telogan階段， HFSCs幹細胞進入「冬眠」狀態，不作任何複製舉動，而毛髮亦會因而自然地脫落。<br />\n<br />\n落入telogan階段後，幹細胞便會再度進入anagen階段，重新開始產生毛髮。<br />\n<br />\n健康人士的HFSCs幹細胞，高達80-90%處於anagen，10-20%處於catagan，只有1-5%處於telogan階段。<br />\n<br />\n由此可以推想出，脫髮或者禿頭的原因就是大多數的HFSCs處於catagan或telogan階段，並不再重返anagen階段。<br />\n<br />\n下集將會講解為何壓力過大會導致脫髮，箇中的原理涉及荷爾蒙的改變，及幹細胞三階段的失衡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=3e6fe8e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=7a6ba990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n <br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26763421/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F26763421%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=a095619b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26763421/</a>"},{"pid":"21f5e4624b3b0d6342744e886c17aba06209728f","tid":2478130,"uid":2901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T21:48:30.000Z","msg":"樓主你係咁早起身定未瞓"},{"pid":"103db4ef88d8b3089c3989b536843e30adf7ac8c","tid":2478130,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21f5e4624b3b0d6342744e886c17aba06209728f","tid":2478130,"uid":2901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T21:48:30.000Z","msg":"樓主你係咁早起身定未瞓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T22:03:11.000Z","msg":"咁妳呢"},{"pid":"7d4d91bdcf611b9274d236fd5fbcec5cd06cb930","tid":2478130,"uid":255980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"